  "title": "Retail Operations Executive #82173",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Retail</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Retail Operations Executive</strong></li><li>Working Location: Chinatown</li><li>Working Hours: 5.5 days (10.00am – 9.00pm)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic salary up to $2,800 + OT + AWS + Variable Bonus</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent Role</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Manage the retail counter and assist customers with enquiries</li><li>Handle daily store operations, stock-taking, and goods receiving</li><li>Monitor inventory levels and support stock replenishment</li><li>Process and pack customer orders from online and walk-in channels</li><li>Prepare orders for logistics pickup with proper checks and documentation</li><li>Support coordination between retail, warehouse, and e-commerce teams</li><li>Assist in occasional events and booth sales</li><li>Provide professional customer service and help resolve customer issues</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum N-Level, O-Level, ITE, or Diploma qualification</li><li>1–2 years of relevant retail, inventory, or e-commerce experience preferred</li><li>Customer-oriented with good communication skills</li><li>Able to multitask in a fast-paced environment</li><li>Basic knowledge of e-commerce platforms is an advantage</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#82173 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Rachael Lee | EA Reg No.: R2093131</p>",
